  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Swing. Climb. Jump.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Swing through ropes and overcome obstacles. It’s all about timing and momentum.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3346790/extras/b39d87d88c35109d52e0481b6ceac881.poster.avif?t=1743438961\" width=528 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3346790/extras/b39d87d88c35109d52e0481b6ceac881.webm?t=1743438961\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3346790/extras/b39d87d88c35109d52e0481b6ceac881.mp4?t=1743438961\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Simple to move, hard to master.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The controls are straightforward, but working with the ropes takes patience and practice.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3346790/extras/b1a4e945323c9699579891e447324e04.poster.avif?t=1743438961\" width=528 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3346790/extras/b1a4e945323c9699579891e447324e04.webm?t=1743438961\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3346790/extras/b1a4e945323c9699579891e447324e04.mp4?t=1743438961\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>What to expect:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Physics-Based Gameplay:</strong> Feel the weight and momentum.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Rage:</strong> Fail, retry, and fail again—until you achieve.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Replayable Fun</strong></i><strong>:</strong> Push for a smooth run and a faster time.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Challenging Environment:</strong> It is actually difficult.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3346790/extras/3624c238026fb29674ea9a2c4ddff810.poster.avif?t=1743438961\" width=528 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3346790/extras/3624c238026fb29674ea9a2c4ddff810.webm?t=1743438961\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3346790/extras/3624c238026fb29674ea9a2c4ddff810.mp4?t=1743438961\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grab the rope and see how far you can go!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Swing. Climb. Jump.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Swing through ropes and overcome obstacles. It’s all about timing and momentum.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3346790/extras/b39d87d88c35109d52e0481b6ceac881.poster.avif?t=1743438961\" width=528 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3346790/extras/b39d87d88c35109d52e0481b6ceac881.webm?t=1743438961\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3346790/extras/b39d87d88c35109d52e0481b6ceac881.mp4?t=1743438961\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Simple to move, hard to master.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The controls are straightforward, but working with the ropes takes patience and practice.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3346790/extras/b1a4e945323c9699579891e447324e04.poster.avif?t=1743438961\" width=528 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3346790/extras/b1a4e945323c9699579891e447324e04.webm?t=1743438961\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3346790/extras/b1a4e945323c9699579891e447324e04.mp4?t=1743438961\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>What to expect:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Physics-Based Gameplay:</strong> Feel the weight and momentum.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Rage:</strong> Fail, retry, and fail again—until you achieve.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Replayable Fun</strong></i><strong>:</strong> Push for a smooth run and a faster time.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Challenging Environment:</strong> It is actually difficult.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3346790/extras/3624c238026fb29674ea9a2c4ddff810.poster.avif?t=1743438961\" width=528 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3346790/extras/3624c238026fb29674ea9a2c4ddff810.webm?t=1743438961\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3346790/extras/3624c238026fb29674ea9a2c4ddff810.mp4?t=1743438961\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grab the rope and see how far you can go!</p>",
